                                 rdfs:label "has last name" .


###  http://purl.org/gc/hasMass
<http://purl.org/gc/hasMass> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ;
                             rdfs:subPropertyOf <http://purl.org/gc/hasMolecularData> .


###  http://purl.org/gc/hasMethod
<http://purl.org/gc/hasMethod> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ;
