                                        rdfs:comment "The upper property for various properties related to the publication data" ;
                                        rdfs:isDefinedBy <http://chemicalsemantics.com/> ;
                                        rdfs:label "Generic Datatype Property for Publication data"@en .


###  http://purl.org/gc/hasQuantumMechanics
<http://purl.org/gc/hasQuantumMechanics> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .


###  http://purl.org/gc/hasSecondaryStructure
