                                 rdfs:comment "A class for Self Consistent Field methods (Hartree-Fock methods) for approximate solution of Schrödinger equation for quantum many body system."@en ;
                                 rdfs:label "Ab initio SCF"@en .


###  http://purl.org/gc/AbinitioScf
